106
00:09:32,790 --> 00:09:34,390
and become friends with you?

107
00:09:44,260 --> 00:09:44,990
Big Brother,

108
00:09:47,110 --> 00:09:48,770
no matter what happens today,

109
00:09:49,680 --> 00:09:51,090
I won't let them die.

110
