117
00:10:10,160 --> 00:10:11,020
Give me an hour.

118
00:10:12,490 --> 00:10:14,020
I'll go beg Lord Chieftain.

119
00:10:14,030 --> 00:10:16,470
Lord Chieftain doesn't like people pleading for traitors.

120
00:10:16,470 --> 00:10:18,070
You'll ruin your own future.

121
00:10:18,110 --> 00:10:18,870
Big Brother,

122
00:10:20,510 --> 00:10:22,150
if I can't even protect

123
00:10:22,150 --> 00:10:23,480
these innocent people,

124
00:10:24,260 --> 00:10:26,520
