171
00:13:43,920 --> 00:13:47,350
If I can't even

172
00:13:47,350 --> 00:13:48,680
save the Palace Guards,

173
00:13:49,830 --> 00:13:51,380
what's the use of having a bright future?

174
00:13:51,380 --> 00:13:53,580
