177
00:14:17,150 --> 00:14:21,300
But my future is not important.

178
00:14:22,190 --> 00:14:23,630
Zichuan's future is more important.

179
00:14:23,630 --> 00:14:25,740
You should know your place, Lin He.

180
00:14:28,000 --> 00:14:29,750
