213
00:16:41,490 --> 00:16:42,530
I told you

214
00:16:43,110 --> 00:16:44,540
I don't care about anyone,

215
00:16:44,540 --> 00:16:45,870
except the three of you.

216
00:16:47,400 --> 00:16:48,200
Xiujia,

217
00:16:48,950 --> 00:16:50,070
Si Yilin,

218
00:16:51,150 --> 00:16:52,190
and you.

219
00:17:05,050 --> 00:17:06,180
